---
title: Creamy Tomato Gnocchi with Hazelnut & Chive Pesto
description: Gnocchi with pesto is an all-time favourite. We've given this version a HelloFresh twist by pan-frying the gnocchi. It gives the pillowy little dumplings a beautifully crisp crust. We've also mixed up the pesto by replacing the usual basil and pine nuts with chives and Hazelnuts. This dish went down a treat at the Fresh Farm and we hope you love it too!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-tomato-gnocchi-f9993b6a-7f04a86f.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/creamy-tomato-gnocchi-594bf2b0d56afa1201024792-0e0d90e5.pdf
